<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Support the Developer — Yumeka</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #1a1a2e;
      --surface: #16213e;
      --card: #0f3460;
      --accent: #e94560;
      --accent-soft: #ff6b9d;
      --text: #ffffff;
      --text-muted: #a0a0b0;
      --text-faint: #505070;
      --radius: 12px;
    }

    body {
      background-color: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3.5rem 0 2.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .logo-kanji {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: var(--accent-soft);
    }

    .logo-latin {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.35em;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .page-title {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent-soft);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }

    /* Hero message */
    .hero-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--card);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 2rem 2rem 1.75rem;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-card .emoji {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .hero-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .hero-card p {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* Donate options */
    .donate-options {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .donate-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--card);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.4rem 1.75rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .donate-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent-soft);
    }

    .donate-card-left {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .donate-icon {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .donate-label {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .donate-sublabel {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 0.1rem;
    }

    .donate-btn {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .donate-card:hover .donate-btn {
      background: var(--accent-soft);
    }

    /* What your support covers */
    .perks-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--card);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .perks-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .perks-list li {
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.65rem;
    }

    .perks-list li .perk-dot {
      color: var(--accent-soft);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 0.1rem;
    }

    /* Note */
    .note {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--text-faint);
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--card);
      color: var(--text-faint);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--text-faint);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      color: var(--accent-soft);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="logo-kanji">夢華</div>
    <div class="logo-latin">Y U M E K A</div>
    <div class="page-title">Support the Developer</div>
  </header>

  <main>

    <div class="hero-card">
      <div class="emoji">♡</div>
      <h2>Yumeka is free — and will stay that way.</h2>
      <p>If you're enjoying the app, a small donation helps cover server costs and keeps Yumeka free and ad-free for everyone.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label">Donate</div>
    <div class="donate-options">

      <a class="donate-card" href="https://paypal.me/katiwada" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <div class="donate-card-left">
          <div class="donate-icon">💙</div>
          <div>
            <div class="donate-label">Donate via PayPal</div>
            <div class="donate-sublabel">One-time donation — any amount appreciated</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="donate-btn">Donate</div>
      </a>

    </div>

    <div class="section-label">What your support covers</div>
    <div class="perks-card">
      <ul class="perks-list">
        <li><span class="perk-dot">▸</span> Supabase database and storage hosting</li>
        <li><span class="perk-dot">▸</span> Keeping the app free with no ads</li>
        <li><span class="perk-dot">▸</span> Ongoing development and bug fixes</li>
        <li><span class="perk-dot">▸</span> New features and improvements</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="note">Donations are voluntary and do not unlock any features.<br />Thank you for being part of Yumeka. 夢華</p>

  </main>

  <footer>
    <a href="/">yumeka.app</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
    <a href="/support.html">Support</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
    <a href="/privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
